Class ServiceMetricsRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.plexobject.metrics.ServiceMetricsRegistry

  • public class ServiceMetricsRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    This class maintains service metrics. It also exposes them as JMX MBeans so that the can be viewed with JConsole.
